Initializes an instance of the WifiInfo class using the specified timestamps, WiFi state, Mac address, rssi, and ssid.

Parameters:
beginTimeStamp - The beginning timestamp for the WiFi event.
endTimeStamp - The ending timestamp for the WiFi event.
wifiState - One of the values of the WiFiState enumeration that indicates the state of the WiFi connection.
macAddress - The WiFi Mac address.
rssi - The RSSI value.
ssid - The SSID value.
